==Transportation==
The center is accessible within walking distance South West from [[Yanchengpu Station]] of [[Kaohsiung MRT]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pier-2.khcc.gov.tw/e_content/traffic/traffic01.aspx |title=Pier-2 Art Center-Getting Here |publisher=Pier-2.khcc.gov.tw |date= |accessdate=2014-04-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502002103/http://pier-2.khcc.gov.tw/e_content/traffic/traffic01.aspx |archivedate=2014-05-02 |df= }}</ref>. 
Since 2017, Dayi Pier-2 Station(駁二大義) and Penglai Pier-2 Station(駁二蓬萊) of [[Circular_light_rail|Kaohsiung LRT]] pass through the Pier-2 Art Center.

